{"type":"message","id":"1fd83c52","parentId":"f716b8ee","timestamp":"2026-04-11T03:30:08.983Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:acdb7218-c2eb-439d-b557-e08df3671301 daily-war-update] Generate daily global conflict update for Nemesis (Indian citizen):\n1. Focus **ONLY** on developments that directly impact India, Indian citizens, economy, travel, oil prices, or regional stability\n2. No generic war updates. No filler. Every point must explain: what happened, what this means for India, what to prepare for\n3. Structure:\n   - ✅ IMPACT ON INDIA\n   - ⚠️ PREPARE / MONITOR\n   - 🛢️ OIL / FUEL PRICES\n   - ✈️ TRAVEL STATUS\n   - 🔮 WHAT HAPPENS NEXT\n4. Keep it concise, practical, actionable. Only send to Nemesis DM. Never post this anywhere else.\n5. End with exactly one sentence summary of what normal people should do today.\nCurrent time: Saturday, April 11th, 2026 - 3:30 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-11 03:30 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775878208965}}
